title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Luck
subTitle: Moussa, a mafia leader, gives a bunch of people an opportunity to earn a hefty amount by making them participate in a game of survival.

title: Badlapur Boys
subTitle: Vijay grows up with a dream of bringing water to his village after his father's sacrifice goes in vain. So, he participates in a kabaddi tournament to attract the attention of the bureaucracy.

title: Saath Saath
subTitle: Gita, a girl from a wealthy family, falls in love with an idealistic Avinash who has stern principles in life. However, his changed behaviour post marriage troubles her.

title: I M 24
subTitle: A 42-year-old writer falls in love with a 22-year-old beauty queen. However, things get complicated when his roommate encourages him to make up stories to impress her.

title: Raja
subTitle: Raju and Madhu are forced apart by the latter's elder brothers, leading to increased distance between the two.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Disco Dancer
subTitle: A slum-dwelling performer finds a new calling as a rising disco star. However, things take an unfortunate turn when an enemy from the past reappears in his life.

title: Auzaar
subTitle: Suraj, a police officer, is assigned to arrest his friend Yash, whose father runs an illegal business. He must now persuade his friend to make his father change his ways to avoid the consequences.

title: Mann
subTitle: Dev and Priya fall in love despite being engaged to their respective partners and decide to reunite after six months to get married. However, destiny has other plans for them.

title: Phullu
subTitle: Phullu's mother decides to marry him off to make him more mature. Things take an unexpected turn when he learns about menstruation after marriage.

title: Nayee Padosan
subTitle: Three men try different methods to woo their neighbour. However, her father wants her to get married to someone from his community.

title: Amar Saheed Bhagat Singh
subTitle: The young and charismatic socialist Bhagat Singh chooses to fight against the atrocities of British rule during India's independence movement, sacrificing his life to become a revolutionary hero.

title: Surkhiyaan (The Headlines)
subTitle: Shera hopes to marry Sapna, but is sent to prison for committing a crime. He is released after several months, only to be arrested again, unaware that he and Sapna are mere pawns in a dangerous game.

title: Road to Sangam
subTitle: A devout Muslim Indian man is tasked with repairing a lorry in order to transport the ashes of Mahatma Gandhi. However, when communal violence strikes, he is left with a troubling dilemma.

title: Officer Arjun Singh IPS
subTitle: Arjun Pratap Singh, an IPS officer, strives to overcome multiple challenges and embarks on a mission to restore peace in society.

title: S.P. Chauhan
subTitle: Satpal Chauhan, a social worker from Haryana, works for women empowerment and also strives to create an alcohol-free society. However, while pursuing his goals, he faces several hardships.

title: Deewaar: Let's Bring Our Heroes Home
subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: I Proud to Be an Indian
subTitle: I, a man from India, travels to London for a family wedding and finds that their community is being threatened by a racist group. Seeing this, he decides to get involved and fight back.

title: Battalion 609
subTitle: Indian and Pakistani armies clash verbally, leading to a cricket match challenge where territorial pride hangs in the balance.

title: Battalion 609
subTitle: Indian and Pakistani armies clash verbally, leading to a cricket match challenge where territorial pride hangs in the balance.

title: 3I 3 Indians
subTitle: Raj, Shahan and Sherdill join a covert operation led by a reformist minister to expose dangerous networks that threaten the country from within.

title: Shool
subTitle: Inspector Samar is transferred to Motihari in Bihar, India, due to his honesty. He soon earns the wrath of a corrupt politician, Bachchu Yadav, who gradually becomes a threat to him and his family.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: When Birju's sister, Chhaya, is raped and the court fails to mete out justice, his parents die due to the shock. Birju sets out to seek revenge and kidnaps Dinanath's sister.

title: Karamdaata
subTitle: Pinky, the granddaughter of a wealthy industrialist, runs away and marries a taxi driver. However, the businessman holds Pinky's lover responsible and gets him arrested.

title: Satta
subTitle: Anuradha relocates to Mumbai where she meets Vivek, an aspiring politician, and marries him. Things take a turn when he is arrested for murder and she has to take his place in the upcoming elections.

title: Bollywood Diaries
subTitle: Three individuals from different backgrounds aspire to make it big in Bollywood but face difficulties as they carve their path.

title: Gone Kesh
subTitle: After being diagnosed with alopecia, a condition that causes rapid hair loss, Enakshi, a young girl, navigates through the trials and tribulations of life.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Soldier
subTitle: After Major Vijay Malhotra's colleagues betray him, he is branded as a traitor and subsequently killed. But his son, Vicky, vows to take revenge on his father's murderers and prove his innocence.

title: Dosti: Friends Forever
subTitle: Karan, a wealthy heir, lives a lonely life and is neglected by his family. When he has a fatal accident, Raj, a poor orphan, saves his life and they become inseparable friends.
